<script type="text/javascript">podPressShowHidePlayer('1', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/3-12/epi-00864-a-conversation-with-jack.mp3', 290, 24, 'false', 'http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress/images/vpreview_center.png', 'Episode-864- A Conversation With Jack', 'The Survival Podcast');</script><p><a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/jackspirko.jpg"><img class="alignleft  wp-image-6212" title="jackspirko" src="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/jackspirko.jpg" alt="" width="140" height="151" /></a>Yep basically today is just me chatting with you.  I have quite a few things I want to cover, go over and some hanging stuff out there I want to kind of &#8220;clean up&#8221;.</p>
<p>I also bring up some topics and ideas that may really challenge your belief and may even make some of you angry with me.  I only ask that you listen to and consider what I say.  I also only ask that if you disagree and I don&#8217;t see things your way that we still respect one another.</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #800000;">Join me Today as we Discuss&#8230;</span></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Follow up on yesterdays <a title="silver" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/episode-51-options-and-reasons-to-invest-in-silver">silver</a> episode</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>An update on the Spirko Homestead</li>
<ul>
<li>The Prepper in the Dog House</li>
<li>The <a target="_blank" title="swales" href="http://tspwiki.com/index.php?title=Swale">swales</a> are going nuts</li>
<li>Trees are in the ground</li>
<li>The garden is off to a great start</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>What is truth and what is opinion</li>
<ul>
<li>The lesson of Backwoods Engineer</li>
<li>A what if scenario that shows the creation of Israel in a different light</li>
<li>How fictions become truth</li>
<li>Why do you trust a source that has been proven wrong so many times</li>
<li>Bashing a government and financial rulers of a nation isn&#8217;t bashing the nation</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Some of the &#8220;truths&#8221; we all have united on</li>
<ul>
<li>The nation is going broke</li>
<li>Politicians are controlled by money &#8211; not voters</li>
<li>Good people are made criminals by pointless laws &#8211; (<a target="_blank" title="Joel Salatin" href="http://tspwiki.com/index.php?title=Joel_Salatin">Joel Salatin</a>)</li>
<li>It is up to us to fix the problems and deal with their aftermath</li>
</ul>
</ul>
