<p>Thanks for your explanation on Zionism.  While your &#8220;Mormon Holocaust&#8221; scenario is a pretty close analogy, it isn&#8217;t (as you stated) an exact one.   It is useful to examine most people&#8217;s feelings on the subject.</p>
